{
  "page": "Dalla (Dragonstone)",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">For Mance Rayder's wife, see <a href=\"/index.php/Dalla\" title=\"Dalla\">Dalla</a>. For the princesses, see <a href=\"/index.php/Daella_Targaryen\" title=\"Daella Targaryen\">Daella Targaryen</a>.</div>\n<table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\">Dalla</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Baratheon_of_Dragonstone\" title=\"House Baratheon of Dragonstone\">House Baratheon of Dragonstone</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Dalla</b> is a serving woman at <a href=\"/index.php/Dragonstone\" title=\"Dragonstone\">Dragonstone</a>. She is in service to <a href=\"/index.php/House_Baratheon_of_Dragonstone\" title=\"House Baratheon of Dragonstone\">House Baratheon of Dragonstone</a>. \n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Dalla_(Dragonstone)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Clash_of_Kings\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Dalla_(Dragonstone)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Clash of Kings\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Dalla and <a href=\"/index.php/Matrice\" title=\"Matrice\">Matrice</a> talk about the <a href=\"/index.php/Red_comet\" title=\"Red comet\">red comet</a>, and Dalla shares that she had heard <a href=\"/index.php/Melisandre\" title=\"Melisandre\">Melisandre</a> tell Queen <a href=\"/index.php/Selyse_Florent\" title=\"Selyse Florent\">Selyse Florent</a> that the comet was \"<a href=\"/index.php/Dragonfire\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Dragonfire\">dragonsbreath</a>\". Princess <a href=\"/index.php/Shireen_Baratheon\" title=\"Shireen Baratheon\">Shireen Baratheon</a> overhears their discussion, and when she worriedly informs <a href=\"/index.php/Maester\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Maester\">Maester</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Cressen\" title=\"Cressen\">Cressen</a>, he thinks he must have a word with Dalla, to warn her not to spread such rumors.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racokprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racokprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Dalla_(Dragonstone)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racokprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racokprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Prologue\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Prologue\">Prologue</a>.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403103233\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.084 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.312 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 365/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10468/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 3613/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 226/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 538/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.210/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.52 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  302.981      1 -total\n 86.09%  260.826      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 85.43%  258.847      1 Template:Infobox\n 11.39%   34.498     12 Template:Infobox_value\n 11.13%   33.707      1 Template:For-multi\n 10.90%   33.033      1 Template:Hatnote\n  2.52%    7.644      2 Template:Infobox_label\n  1.99%    6.031      1 Template:Ref\n  1.32%    3.995      1 Template:Ref/core\n  0.70%    2.108      1 Template:References\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:3404-0!canonical and timestamp 20260403103232 and revision id 311397\n -->\n",
